title: poppy s?
body: played poppy. 11/0/23 212 farm 50 mins. didnt get an S it has to be my farm right?

replies.body: There are a few factors involved here, like the role that you selected for Poppy.  I mean, that farm seems pretty good!  There just may be other Poppy's performing better right now.  Be sure to check out our [champion mastery](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204211284-Champion-Mastery-Guide) guide for more info, and don't give up!
